Package: rbiostatistics
Title: R Biostatistics Analysis Tools for Clinical and Epidemiological Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gabriel", "Demetrios Lafis", email = "gabriel.lafis@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive package for biostatistical analysis in clinical and epidemiological research.
    The package provides tools for survival analysis, clinical trials, epidemiological studies,
    meta-analysis, and biomarker evaluation. Features include Kaplan-Meier estimation, Cox proportional
    hazards models, competing risks analysis, ROC curve analysis, and various epidemiological measures
    such as relative risk, odds ratio, and attributable risk.
